    "---\n",
    "## 7. Mispricing Detection\n",
    "\n",
    "Identify strikes where the market IV deviates significantly from the Heston fair value.\n",
    "We use a z-score approach: \n",
    "\n",
    "$$z_i = \\frac{IV_{\\text{mkt},i} - IV_{\\text{Heston},i}}{\\sigma_{\\text{residuals}}}$$"
   ]
