market IV too low): {(mispricing_df[\\\"mispricing_type\\\"] == \\\"underpriced\\\").sum()}\")\\n',\n    'print(f\"  Fair: {(mispricing_df[\\\"mispricing_type\\\"] == \\\"fair\\\").sum()}\")\\n',\n    '\\n',\n    '# Show most mispriced options\\n',
